{"tid":710762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國教科書稱女生衣著暴露是對男人性騷擾","createTime":"2018-06-21T04:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T10:48:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2cdec82ef4926ace5a550d08e9f6aa351401ea84","tid":710762,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpJy4FSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpJy4FSB.jpg&h=aa5531ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國黑龍江教育出版社出版的《高中生公共安全教育讀本》，稱女性在公共場所穿著暴露，對男性是「首當其衝的性騷擾」，引發輿論譁然。黑龍江教育出版社回應，指已經將所有書籍召回，並向公眾致歉。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，該讀本第6頁引述心理學家對女性有性騷擾男性嫌疑的定義，包含衣著暴露、言行不端、肢體摩擦和碰撞等。其中一條寫道，「女性在公共場所穿著暴露，乃至衣不蔽體，對男性是首當其衝的性騷擾。」引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n黑龍江教育出版社回應，表示確實存在內容不夠嚴謹、審稿不嚴等問題，已經在最新的版本中，將相關內容刪去。而這一版本是針對黑龍江牡丹江地區的特色編寫，只向牡丹江市的學校發放幾百冊，將全部收回。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2445252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2445252&d=sezGOmjLrfSMKGOZkk38vDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b8cdc227\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2445252&h=2e31a4c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2445252</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f2d1afaea2e454f4eca08b7db9c4c154a75b42","tid":710762,"uid":47268,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"幾時性騷擾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7421135650855d17c7d37e296f3b725687c13c2b","tid":710762,"uid":60363,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"樣衰嘅咪性騷擾囉"},{"pid":"1b41eca291df9175e29169281d3afd6a515ea4d8","tid":710762,"uid":77196,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"